<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler.FilterMode" Title="FilterMode enumeration" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler">ITextureSampler</PageRef> ->
    FilterMode
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterMode</TypeRef> enumeration defines how samples are filtered within a mipmap level when a texture is magnified or minified. It is configured with <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler.SetTextureFilterMode">SetTextureFilterMode</PageRef>.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <EnumMemberList>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Nearest">
        Uses the nearest texel value without interpolation.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
      <EnumMemberListEntry Name="Linear">
        Interpolates between neighbouring texel values.
      </EnumMemberListEntry>
    </EnumMemberList>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureSampler.SetTextureFilterMode">ITextureSampler.SetTextureFilterMode</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
